s in this round.\n    #[max_len(20)]\n    pub players: Vec<PlayerEntry>,\n    /// Total entries across all players.\n    pub total_entries: u32,\n    /// Unix timestamp when the round was created.\n    pub created_at: i64,\n    /// Unix timestamp when countdown ends (0 if not yet started).\n    pub countdown_ends_at: i64,\n    /// Unix timestamp when the round entered Locked phase (0 if not yet).\n    pub locked_at: i64,\n    /// Deadline for VRF resolution; after this, timeout refund is available.\n    pub resolve_deadline: i64,\n    /// Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time.\n    pub vrf_request_key: Pubkey,\n    /// The winning slot index (only valid after settlement).\n    pub winning_slot: u32,\n    /// The winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled).\n    pub winner: Pubkey,\n    /// Whether the payout has been claimed.\n    pub claimed: bool,\n    /// The creator of the round (receives rent back on close).\n    pub creator: Pubkey,\n    /// Bump seed for PDA derivation.\n    pub bump: u8,\n}\n\n/// Event emitted when a round is settled via claim_payout.\n#[event]\npub struct RoundSettled {\n    /// Tier index.\n    pub tier: u8,\n    /// Round number.\n    pub round_number: u64,\n    /// Winner's wallet address.\n    pub winner: Pubkey,\n    /// Raw VRF randomness bytes.\n    pub randomness: [u8; 32],\n    /// The winning slot index (0-based).\n    pub winning_slot: u32,\n    /// Total entries in the round.\n    pub total_entries: u32,\n    /// Net payout to winner (after fee).\n    pub payout_amount: u64,\n    /// Platform fee amount.\n    pub fee_amount: u64,\n    /// Address of the Orao VRF request PDA.\n    pub vrf_request_key: Pubkey,\n}\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
