{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014opCev7TugW3w4p57zPxQk","type":"tool_result","content":"   212→### Implementation Checklist\n   213→\n   214→#### Phase A: On-Chain Program (Lord of the RNGs)\n   215→\n   216→- [ ] [on-chain] Scaffold `solana/programs/lordofrngs/` — Cargo.toml, Xargo.toml, `src/lib.rs` with `declare_id!`, `src/state.rs` with `LordConfig` + `JackpotRound` + `PlayerEntry` + `RoundSettled` event, `src/error.rs` with error codes. Register in `solana/Cargo.toml` workspace members and `Anchor.toml` programs. Verify: `anchor build -p lordofrngs` succeeds.\n   217→- [ ] [on-chain] `initialize_config` instruction — admin creates `LordConfig` PDA (`[b\"lord_config\"]`) with treasury + authority + paused flag. Pattern: copy from coinflip `initialize_config.rs`. Verify: bankrun test creates config, reads back fields.\n   218→- [ ] [on-chain] `create_round` instruction — creates `JackpotRound` PDA (`[b\"jackpot_round\", tier, round_number]`). Caller pays rent and is first player. Sets phase=Waiting, records entry, transfers entry_amount lamports to round PDA escrow. Requires: config not paused, valid tier (0–5), round_number from a counter on LordConfig. Verify: bankrun test creates round, checks PDA data + escrow balance.\n   219→- [ ] [on-chain] `join_round` instruction — new player joins an existing round. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active (countdown), player not already in round, player count < 20. Adds PlayerEntry to Vec, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. If this is the 2nd unique player, transition phase Waiting→Active and set `countdown_ends_at = clock + 60`. Verify: bankrun tests for happy path (join triggers countdown), duplicate player rejection, max players rejection, wrong phase rejection.\n   220→- [ ] [on-chain] `buy_more_entries` instruction — existing player buys additional entries. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active, player already in round. Increments player's entry count, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. Verify: bankrun test buys more, checks updated entry count + pool.\n   221→- [ ] [on-chain] `start_spin` instruction — permissionless, idempotent. Validates: phase is Active, `clock.unix_timestamp >= countdown_ends_at`. If phase is already Locked, return Ok (idempotent no-op, no error). Transitions phase Active→Locked, requests Orao VRF (CPI). Records `vrf_request_key`. Verify: bankrun tests — happy path (phase transition + VRF request), idempotent re-call (no error when already Locked), too early rejection (countdown not expired), wrong phase rejection."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63a7d9fb-5b39-41e7-af6f-c6c9731af600","uuid":"f53ff484-a147-4a33-8fbb-63b972cefa3c","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/101-lord-of-the-rngs/spec.md","content":"### Implementation Checklist\n\n#### Phase A: On-Chain Program (Lord of the RNGs)\n\n- [ ] [on-chain] Scaffold `solana/programs/lordofrngs/` — Cargo.toml, Xargo.toml, `src/lib.rs` with `declare_id!`, `src/state.rs` with `LordConfig` + `JackpotRound` + `PlayerEntry` + `RoundSettled` event, `src/error.rs` with error codes. Register in `solana/Cargo.toml` workspace members and `Anchor.toml` programs. Verify: `anchor build -p lordofrngs` succeeds.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `initialize_config` instruction — admin creates `LordConfig` PDA (`[b\"lord_config\"]`) with treasury + authority + paused flag. Pattern: copy from coinflip `initialize_config.rs`. Verify: bankrun test creates config, reads back fields.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `create_round` instruction — creates `JackpotRound` PDA (`[b\"jackpot_round\", tier, round_number]`). Caller pays rent and is first player. Sets phase=Waiting, records entry, transfers entry_amount lamports to round PDA escrow. Requires: config not paused, valid tier (0–5), round_number from a counter on LordConfig. Verify: bankrun test creates round, checks PDA data + escrow balance.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `join_round` instruction — new player joins an existing round. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active (countdown), player not already in round, player count < 20. Adds PlayerEntry to Vec, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. If this is the 2nd unique player, transition phase Waiting→Active and set `countdown_ends_at = clock + 60`. Verify: bankrun tests for happy path (join triggers countdown), duplicate player rejection, max players rejection, wrong phase rejection.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `buy_more_entries` instruction — existing player buys additional entries. Validates: phase is Waiting or Active, player already in round. Increments player's entry count, transfers entry_amount × entries to escrow. Verify: bankrun test buys more, checks updated entry count + pool.\n- [ ] [on-chain] `start_spin` instruction — permissionless, idempotent. Validates: phase is Active, `clock.unix_timestamp >= countdown_ends_at`. If phase is already Locked, return Ok (idempotent no-op, no error). Transitions phase Active→Locked, requests Orao VRF (CPI). Records `vrf_request_key`. Verify: bankrun tests — happy path (phase transition + VRF request), idempotent re-call (no error when already Locked), too early rejection (countdown not expired), wrong phase rejection.","numLines":10,"startLine":212,"totalLines":272}}}
